<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="SB0215" sponsor="Stephanie Pitcher" designation="SB" otherSponsor="" otherHouse="House" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL1355" date="1/28/2026 13:01:637" printDate="01-28 13:23" subVer="0" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>12</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="05/06/2026"><seclist><sect action="A" src="code" buid="1" uid="C78B-6-S852_2026050620260506" fromuid="C78B-6-S852_2022050420220701" sort="78B06 08520020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">78B-6-852</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="11" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Eviction Record Amendments</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Stephanie Pitcher</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>House Sponsor: </otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill modifies provisions related to the expungement of evictions.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1"> modifies the time period required before an automatic expungement of an eviction takes <ln numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9"/>place; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10" level="1">makes technical and conforming changes.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="12">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="14">None</ocNone><sa numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saamd numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16"><snhead>AMENDS:</snhead><sn num="78B-6-852" src="code" uid="C78B-6-S852_2026050620260506" buid="1" sort="78B06 08520020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17"><bold>78B-6-852</bold>, as enacted by Laws of Utah 2022, Chapter 372</sn></saamd></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="18"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="1" num="78B-6-852" type="amend" src="code" uid="C78B-6-S852_2026050620260506" sort="78B06 08520020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section number="78B-6-852" numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="1-2" type="amend"><secline lineno="20">Section 1. Section <bold>78B-6-852</bold> is amended to read:</secline><catline lineno="21"><bold>78B-6-852<parens/>. Automatic expungement of eviction.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="1-null-1" dnum="1-o" numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="1-3" level="1" placement="noreturn" space="false"><display>(1)</display><subsection ssid="1-null-2" dnum="a-o:_-i" ea="erase" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="2" level="2" placement="sameline"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1001" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(a)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/></display>Without the filing of a petition, a court shall order expungement of all records of <ln numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-4"/>an eviction if:<subsection ssid="1-null-3" dnum="i-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-5" level="2" tab="1" space="false"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1002" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(i)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start" space="true">(a)</amend></display><subsection ssid="1-10" dnum="_-o:i-i" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3" placement="sameline"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="end">(i)</amend></display>the entire case was dismissed;</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-4" dnum="ii-o" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-6" level="3"><display>(ii)</display>there is no appeal pending for the case; and</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-5" dnum="iii-o" numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-7" level="3"><display>(iii)</display>at least <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="8" groupid="6" style="2" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" deltag="both">three years</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="6" groupid="4" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">90 days</amend> have passed from the day on which the eviction was <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="9" groupid="7" style="2" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" deltag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-8"/>filed</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="7" groupid="5" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">dismissed</amend>; or</subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-6" dnum="b-o" numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-9" level="2"><display>(b)</display>the parties to the eviction stipulated to expungement and have filed a stipulation with <ln numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-10"/>the court.</subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-7" dnum="2-o" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-11" level="1"><display>(2)</display>The court shall issue an order of expungement when the court determines that an <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-12"/>eviction qualifies for automatic expungement under Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="78B-6-852(1)" start="0">(1)</xref>.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-8" dnum="3-o" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-13" level="1"><display>(3)</display>This section applies to evictions filed on or after July 1, 2022.</subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="11" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="33">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="34"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="5/6/2026">May 6, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>1-28-26 1:23 PM</tm></rev></foot></leg>